    public class MainActivityUITest
extends android.test.ActivityInstrumentationTestCase2<LoginActivity>
    Created by Boris on 12/03/2017. This class starts in the login screen, logs in and attempts to do a series of tests involving making a mood, editing, deleting and other various functions off of the MainActivity. Now holds a suite of tests for testing most functionality
